public class TagsMenuItem
extends TriStateCheckMenuItem

Returns the tag menu item. These menu items are attached to the menu in the TagsMenuButton.
Each TagsMenuItem carries the names of a tag. Clicking on the name of the tag will tag fires thee ToApplyTag event. There is a X button provided next to every tag to remove the tag from selected requests. Clicking on the X button fires the ToRemoveTag event.
